Usage: specifyPartition [-help] <partitionSpecFileName> [-noEqualizePtnHInst]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
<partitionSpecFileName>     # Specifies the file containing the partition
                            # specification. (string, required)
-noEqualizePtnHInst         # Disables snapping capability of clone partitions
                            # to power grid, such that clones donot necessarily
                            # have same row structure and pattern as their
                            # master. (bool, optional)